 27-year-old's return\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"her signature skills\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was on the vault -the apparatus that led to her dramatic withdrawalfrom individual events in Tokyo - where Biles unleashed the Biles II, becoming the first woman to land the Yurchenko double-pike at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999778516050242, \"rank\": 2.2111222923904453e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault -the apparatus\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"her dramatic withdrawalfrom individual events\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the Biles II\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was not just back but better than ever, even landing her historic Biles IIwith strapping on her left leg.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"her historic Biles IIwith\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"her left leg\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An awkward landing in one of her practice routines left a slight limp and may have sparked some deja vu and concerns of further drama surrounding the American star.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"score\": 0.9999999926321834, \"rank\": 7.367620789286567e-09, \"text\": \"American star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An awkward landing\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"her practice routines\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"a slight limp\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"some deja vu\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"further drama\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was notable, perhaps, that Biles then did not commit to a further unique skill on her uneven bars routine, after submitting plans to do so on Friday.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"a further unique skill\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"her uneven bars\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles picked herself up anyway to firmly establish herself as the favourite for gold in the majority of events in which she will be competing, dominating her session while setting the highest scores on the floor and vault that are unlikely to be beaten throughout the remainder of qualifying.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"the favourite\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"her session\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest scores\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"the remainder\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Biles made a perfect landing on her final routine, on the uneven bars, she broke into a huge smile: from the lows of Tokyo, this was a triumph in every sense.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999778516050242, \"rank\": 2.2111222923904453e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect landing\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"her final routine\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge smile\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the lows\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"a triumph\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"every sense\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles had nothing to prove after making her spectacular, and sudden, return to competition at last year's world championships in Antwerp.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2155, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"score\": 0.9999998443868329, \"rank\": 1.5469708358453088e-07, \"text\": \"Antwerp\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"sudden, return\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's world championships\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympics are different, bringing a level of attention and scrutiny that is unlike anything within the sport's usual parameters.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"a level\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's usual parameters\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, the stars were out to watch Biles, Ariana Grande, Lady Gaga, Tom Cruise and Snoop Dogg among them, as rows of photographers directed their lenses on her as she emerged with a black jacket covering a dazzling sequinned costume - at the cost of $3,000 (\\u00a32,300) for each member of the USA team.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.7741794784784545e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 2360, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q