le somersault and beamed to the crowd, however, it was clear that the most decorated gymnast had left the \\\"twisties\\\" behind.\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"a double somersault\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated gymnast\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The distorting condition that disrupted her previous Games and led to a 732-day absence from major competitions was banished with a display of dazzling power.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The distorting condition\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"her previous Games\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"a 732-day absence\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"major competitions\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"a display\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"dazzling power\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the floor routine, Biles landed one of her six named skills, the Biles II, featuring an explosive triple-twisting double-tuck.\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor routine\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"her six named skills\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"the Biles II\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"an explosive triple-twisting double-tuck\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The centrepiece was the vault: as Biles set a score of 15.300 that was almost a full point ahead of her closest competition, American teammate Jade Carey.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The centrepiece\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3509}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"a full point\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"her closest competition\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the individual all-around standings, Biles finished almost three points clear of Sunisa Lee, her American teammate and defending all-around champion.\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3719, \"end\": 3729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 3735, \"end\": 3743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999671056342508, \"rank\": 3.2720755829591845e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the individual all-around standings\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"all-around champion\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it's about Olympics history.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics history\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 27, Biles would become the oldest American women to win an Olympic gold in gymnastics, breaking the previous record by five years.\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3860, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999671056342508, \"rank\": 3.2720755829591845e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q625